name: HRMIS_2: Verify that the 'Basic Info' accordion expands, and validate the update and close functionalities.
fullName: HRMIS_2: Verify that the 'Basic Info' accordion expands, and validate the update and close functionalities.

steps.name: assert expected **.overlay** not to exist in the DOM
assert expected **[data-testid=**'three-dots-svg'**]** not to exist in the DOM
assert expected **.overlay** not to exist in the DOM
assert expected **<input>** to have value **Autom Mation Ffff**
log Clicked on the Basic Info Option
assert expected **<button.accordion-button>** to have attribute **aria-expanded** with the value **true**
assert Value for First Name: expected **Autom** not to be null
assert Value for Middle Name: expected **Mation** not to be null
assert Value for Last Name: expected **Ffff** not to be null
assert Value for Employee Id: expected **CCIT/10_23/347** not to be null
assert Value for Email: expected **preeti.c@caeliusconsulting.com** not to be null
log Clicked on the Edit button
log Clicked on the Close Button
assert Value for First Name: expected **Autom** not to be null
assert Value for Middle Name: expected **Mation** not to be null
assert Value for Last Name: expected **Ffff** not to be null
assert Value for Employee Id: expected **CCIT/10_23/347** not to be null
assert Value for Email: expected **preeti.c@caeliusconsulting.com** not to be null
log Clicked on the Edit button
log Clicked on the Update Button
assert expected **[data-testid=**'three-dots-svg'**]** not to exist in the DOM
assert Value for First Name: expected **Autom** not to be null
assert Value for Middle Name: expected **Mation** not to be null
assert Value for Last Name: expected **Ffff** not to be null
assert Value for Employee Id: expected **CCIT/10_23/347** not to be null
assert Value for Email: expected **preeti.c@caeliusconsulting.com** not to be null
log Clicked on the Basic Info Option
